♪The best is yet to come♪

570
00:43:10,886 --> 00:43:12,209
♪Isn't it magical♪

571
00:43:12,209 --> 00:43:13,841
♪Listen, look,
how beautiful the night is♪

572
00:43:13,873 --> 00:43:16,340
♪With countless lights on,
is someone heartbroken again♪

573
00:43:16,340 --> 00:43:18,793
♪The sound of a heart
shattering on the ground is so crisp♪

574
00:43:18,874 --> 00:43:21,522
♪Turn on a light.
A lonely heart needs comfort♪

575
00:43:21,611 --> 00:43:24,142
♪Sweat, toil, dawn, dusk♪

576
00:43:24,222 --> 00:43:26,444
♪Devaluing self-respect
just for some hot food♪

577
00:43:26,586 --> 00:43:27,667
