578
00:43:27,776 --> 00:43:30,042
♪Sell dignity at a price,
trampling on past vows♪

579
00:43:30,158 --> 00:43:31,223
♪Until 3 AM♪

580
00:43:31,394 --> 00:43:32,599
♪Locking dreams away in a drawer♪

581
00:43:32,753 --> 00:43:33,986
♪Just to earn some meager profit♪

582
00:43:34,077 --> 00:43:36,441
♪No matter how hard I try,
it only brings sobs♪

583
00:43:36,588 --> 00:43:40,998
♪Renewing yearly, gone with no return,
teetering, utterly bland♪

584
00:43:55,723 --> 00:43:57,159
♪Leave all behind you♪

585
00:43:57,263 --> 00:43:59,750
♪Gotta go on to better things♪

586
00:43:59,933 --> 00:44:02,062
♪You know how far you've gone♪

587
00:44:02,249 --> 00:44:04,589
♪In the fire you rise again♪

588
00:44:04,657 --> 00:44:06,923
♪You made it through the worst♪

589
00:44:07,283 --> 00:44:09,361
♪The best is yet to come♪

590
00:44:09,610 --> 00:44:11,780
♪The best is yet to come♪

591
00:44:14,481 --> 00:44:15,633
♪Isn't it magical♪

592
00:44:15,633 --> 00:44:19,279
♪All the stars are out tonight♪

593
00:44:19,313 --> 00:44:21,169
♪And I see them sparkling♪

594
00:44:21,393 --> 00:44:23,524
♪Nobody knows♪

595
00:44:24,145 --> 00:44:26,055
♪What tomorrow brings♪

596
00:44:26,321 --> 00:44:28,644
♪You made it through the worst♪

597
00:44:28,831 --> 00:44:31,039
♪The best is yet to come♪

598
00:44:31,326 --> 00:44:33,475
♪The best is yet to come♪

599
00:44:33,771 --> 00:44:35,185
♪Isn't it magical♪

600
00:44:35,185 --> 00:44:37,397
♪Feeling uneasy,
yet no one's chasing me♪

601
00:44:37,471 --> 00:44:39,825
♪Retreating step by step,
everything turning to ash♪

602
00:44:39,825 --> 00:44:40,913
♪I'm silent, I'm roaring♪

603
00:44:40,913 --> 00:44:44,364
♪This helplessness
keeps pushing me towards the cliff♪

604
00:44:44,817 --> 00:44:47,091
♪Trembling legs
carry away a shattered soul♪

605
00:44:47,505 --> 00:44:48,369
♪Who wants to be just a passerby♪

606
00:44:48,369 --> 00:44:49,889
♪Isn't it magical♪
